      "id": "PopularPost351185",
      "post_content": "the whole \"Keeper\" Cycle that matches the [Oath](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Oath)s are automatically fair and have long-lasting power to remain relevant in both Multiplayer and Casual for basically EVER ^\\_^   \n  \n  \nthey are the card \" [Balance](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Balance) \" as it SHOULD have been. they'll always be worth it for the first activation as a way to help you come back from behind :D   \n  \nnot Legacy playable like the Oaths, but still fantastic Design.",
